This is an exercise that I did for a job interview in August 2015. The task was to programmatically invoke Cassandra DB's stress tool and to record a few metrics at periodic intervals. Thisproject makes use of multiithreading and Java Management Extensions (JMX).

abstract.doc - The description of the project files
console_output.txt - The output to the console as test ran
JMXmetrics.html - The test results
